Here are some of the more usefull edm screens for motors

motorx.edl  		Motor-control screen with menu for other screens
motorx_tiny.edl  	Tiny motor-control screen
motorx_more.edl  	Medium motor-control screen
motorx_setup.edl 	Setup screen for a single motor
motorx_all.edl  	Debug screen for a single motor
motorx_help.edl  	Help screen for motors

Launch via:
	edm -x -m "P=XXX:,M=m1" motorx.edl
where XXX:m1 is the name of a motor record in an IOC.
